    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/44563749bc3beaa2b185c3908738f3b0.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=600 height=85 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/44563749bc3beaa2b185c3908738f3b0.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款rogue-lite双摇杆射击游戏《City of Beats》中，一切都由无处不在的音乐驱动。聆听节拍、掌握节奏、在城市屋顶上释放枪林弹雨并炸毁城成群结队的敌对仿生人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不必担心对环境造成伤害。人类早已离开，只有仿生人还留在这里。准确来说，是仿生人，机器人，后者一个脾气暴躁的失控人工智能——给时者——所控制，其试图统治所有机器人与仿生人。我们需要一位英雄去把他的插座拔了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/c819c8ca522d0f3fdd1f0021ab755dc8.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=600 height=85 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/c819c8ca522d0f3fdd1f0021ab755dc8.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐驱动一切。任何东西。武器、敌人、环境危害，全都与潜在的节拍息息相关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细聆听音乐以预测攻击、计算躲避时及避开陷阱，还可透过音乐掌握开火、使用特别技能、施放蓄力超级攻击之时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握节拍的流动以及在摩天大楼上流利舞蹈，你将势不可挡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/d2ee7b8e69804d516708ac573b7e44fe.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/d2ee7b8e69804d516708ac573b7e44fe.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/d2ee7b8e69804d516708ac573b7e44fe.mp4?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/18184570296c5634b7f2ce135539aa7b.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=600 height=85 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/18184570296c5634b7f2ce135539aa7b.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在电脑生成的地图上进行无尽的探险。每次冒险不一样——不同的敌人、遭遇与升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏试验不同的装备搭配。今晚，节拍会带来什么？伤害调整？护盾增强？使战斗流程改头换面的突变体？只有音乐知道答案！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与时髦的朋友们组成管弦乐团。失控的维修机器人要倒大霉了！出乎意料城市的商人！不老实的机器骨锯想用非法升级换取的你的能源！节拍汇集了各行各业的合成生命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/bd26b244e2cc4a194de1a2e6fb5b19c7.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/bd26b244e2cc4a194de1a2e6fb5b19c7.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/bd26b244e2cc4a194de1a2e6fb5b19c7.mp4?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/449b3be281dc1c35a2f70d1aaca6da3c.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=600 height=85 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/449b3be281dc1c35a2f70d1aaca6da3c.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只有一条命，但是不用担心——毁灭对机器来说只是有些不方便而已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回到信标塔、升级核心特质、购买新武器并装备扩展包，并确保在下一首歌开始前舒展身体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/2be218761ec90202058ed2a383f2a91e.poster.avif?t=1771529129\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1470390/extras/2be218761ec90202058ed2a383f2a91e.webm?t=1771529129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
